<ul dir="auto">
<li>HTML Sitemap: HTML sitemaps are mainly generated for human use. An HTML Sitemap is a webpage containing links to all the pages of the website. These links are organized hierarchically or categorically for easy navigation to the human user.</li>
</ul>
